接口 IMessageType

  • 所有已知子接口:
    IBundleMessageType, IPersistMessageType
    所有已知实现类:
    AbstractBundleMessageType

    public interface IMessageType
    identity message type which use in different component
    作者:
    dailey_dai

    • 方法概要

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      java.lang.String value()
      return this message type which belong any component;
      such as log message, exception message;
      By implement bundle, the result must match the format:[type:]<full-path>.

    • 方法详细资料

      • value

        java.lang.String value()
        return this message type which belong any component;
        such as log message, exception message;
        By implement bundle, the result must match the format:[type:]<full-path>.
        For example, Log:resource/i18n/Log
        返回:
        String
